Class MainScreenController

java.lang.Object
ViewController.MainScreenController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class MainScreenController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Author:
Nyssa Robinson Main Screen Application Controller initializes the UI This class is the main controller that allows control logic for the Main Screen to navigate to other controllers and populate table views.
